description: These clinics provide comprehensive primary care services to all patients, regardless of a person’s ability to pay. Please note that unless indicated, only Hospital Emergency Departments within a hospital necessarily treat patients regardless of their ability to pay. Check with the individual clinic for their specific financial policies and how they are applied.
